folder
******


Description
===========

A generic term used in the data catalog for an external organization
concept used for a collection of data entities or processes within a
data asset. This term is an internal term which models multiple
external types of folder, such as file directories, database schemas,
and so on. Some data assets, such as Object Store containers, may
contain many levels of folders.


Available Commands
==================

* create

* delete

* get

* list

* update
